8\"></path></svg></span>Não é para ti se…</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-muted/80 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-white/30 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✗</span>Só queres o site feito e não te importas que fique parado no tempo.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-muted/80 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-white/30 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✗</span>Preferes resolver tudo à última hora, quando algo parte.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-muted/80 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-white/30 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✗</span>Não valorizas SEO nem conteúdo de forma contínua.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-muted/80 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-white/30 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✗</span>Procuras um compromisso de zero acompanhamento.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24\" aria-labelledby=\"processo\"><div class=\"hidden lg:block\"><div style=\"height:260vh\" class=\"relative\"><div class=\"sticky top-0 h-screen flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-[640px] mx-auto px-6 mb-8 xl:mb-10\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">Como funciona</p><h2 id=\"processo\" class=\"text-white\">Simples de começar, fácil de manter</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed\">Escolhes o plano e esqueces o assunto — eu trato do digital, mês após mês.</p></div><div class=\"max-w-[1080px] mx-auto w-full px-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[330px] mx-auto\" style=\"height:420px;perspective:1100px\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 h-[3px] rounded-full\" style=\"bottom:-31px;width:63%;opacity:0.3;background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.8)\"></div><div aria-hidden=\"tru