ansform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">Planos</p><h2 id=\"precoh\" class=\"text-white\">Escolhe o teu plano mensal</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Sem fidelização. Começa onde fizer sentido e sobe à medida que cresces.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-white/10 bg-[#0c0d10] p-3 sm:p-4 md:p-5\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_minmax(0,440px)] gap-3 sm:gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[22px] bg-bg-card/40 p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dark mb-7\">Incluído em todos os pacotes</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-7\"><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Manutenção &amp; backups</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">O teu site atualizado, seguro e com cópias de segurança. Dormes descansado.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 12h4l3 8 4-16 3 8h4\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Monitorização 24/7</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Vigio se o site está no ar a toda a hora — se algo falhar, ajo antes de notares.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 17l6-6 4 4 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M16 7h5v5\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">SEO contínuo</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Ajustes e otimização mensais para continuares a subir no Google — não a cair.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M4 4h16v16H4z\"></path><path d=\"M8 9h8M8 13h8M8 17h5\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Conteúdo &amp; posts</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Conteúdo regular para o site e redes (conforme o plano) — presença sempre fresca.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 3v18h18\"></path><path d=\"m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Relatórios mensais</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Um resumo simples todos os meses: o que foi feito e como estás a evoluir.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M21 11.5a8 8 0 0 1-11.5 7.2L4 20l1.3-5.4A8 8 0 1 1 21 11.5Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Suporte prioritário</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Falas comigo diretamente e as tuas alterações têm prioridade. Sem filas.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-auto pt-8\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-2\"><span class=\"flex gap-0.5 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[12px] text-white/80\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\">5,0</span> no Google · 7 avaliações</span></div></div></div><div class=\"relative rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#191d24] via-[#121419] to-[#0c0d10] p-6 sm:p-7 shadow-[0_30px_70px_-30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)] overflow-hidden\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-20 -right-16 w-60 h-60 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 60% 40%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-6 min-h-[28px]\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent font-medium\">Recomendado</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-muted\">por mês · sem fidelização</span></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em]\">Crescimento</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed min-h-[40px]\">Manutenção + SEO e conteúdo para continuares a subir.</p><div class=\"mt-5\"><span class=\"text-white font-heading text-[40px] leading-none font-medium tracking-[-0.02em]\">197€</span></div><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Tudo do Essencial</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>SEO técnico mensal</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Analytics &amp; acompanhamento</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Alguns posts de conteúdo</li></ul></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-dark mb-3\">Escolhe o pacote</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Manutenção</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-accent/50 bg-accent/15 text-white\">Crescimento</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Performance</button></div></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body w-full\" href=\"/contacto?servico=Planos%20Mensais\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Começar agora</span></a></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-accent\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Orçamento e diagnóstico gratuitos</p></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"mt-8 text-center text-[11px] text-dark\">Cada plano inclui tudo o que está no anterior. Podes mudar de plano a qualquer momento.</p></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"faq\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Tenho de assinar por quanto tempo? Posso cancelar?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sem fidelização. É mês a mês — continuas comigo enquanto fizer sentido para ti, e cancelas quando quiseres.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Posso mudar de plano?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sim, a qualquer momento. Subimos ou descemos de plano conforme a fase e as necessidades do teu negócio.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Preciso de ter um site feito por ti?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Não obrigatoriamente. Posso assumir a manutenção de um site existente — faço primeiro uma avaliação para garantir que está em condições.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"As alterações ao site estão incluídas?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Pequenas alterações e atualizações regulares estão incluídas. Mudanças grandes (novas secções, funcionalidades) levam orçamento à parte, sempre transparente e aprovado por ti.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Qual a diferença entre os planos?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sobem em camadas: Essencial = manutenção e segurança; Crescimento = + SEO e conteúdo; Performance = + social e email marketing. Cada plano inclui tudo o que está no anterior.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Como começo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Escolhes um plano ou pedes-me ajuda a escolher no formulário. Respondo em menos de 2 horas, sem compromisso.\"}}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-[820px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">FAQ</p><h2 id=\"faq\" class=\"text-white\">Perguntas frequentes sobre os planos</h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-accent/30 bg-bg-card\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-0\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white\">Tenho de assinar por quanto tempo? Posso cancelar?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-0\"></span></span></button></h3><div id=\"faq-a-0\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"faq-q-0\" class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:auto;opacity:1\"><p class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Sem fidelização. É mês a mês — continuas comigo enquanto fizer sentido para ti, e cancelas quando quiseres.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-1\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Posso mudar de plano?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-2\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Preciso de ter um site feito por ti?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-3\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">As alterações ao site estão incluídas?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-4\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Qual a diferença entre os planos?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-5\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg tra